----------------------

<http://hasseg.org/peg-markdown-highlight/>

Markdown parser for syntax highlighting.

Copyright 2011 Ali Rantakari -- <http://hasseg.org>

PEG-Markdown-Highlight is licensed under the same terms as peg-markdown (see
below for more information).

