Used stuff, currently:

 * [Android][1]
 * [PegJS][2]
 * [Improved Markdown PegC][3] from [Ali Rantakari][4], it used [PEG-Markdown][5] itself for source
 * [Mozilla Rhino][6], adapted to Android, from Android Scripting Layer
 * [NodeJS][7]
 * [Markdown][8]
 * [PHP Markdown Extra][9]

Plan to use:

 * [CodeMirror2][10]
